Gary. are you sleeping?

467
00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:42.973
                   Wah-pa!

468
00:20:43.008 --> 00:20:45.476
Oh. okay. We're good.           
   Don't mind me.

469
00:20:45.511 --> 00:20:47.478
   I'm -- I'm just              
 floating this way.

470
00:20:47.513 --> 00:20:49.046
   This is the way              
    I like to go.

471
00:20:49.081 --> 00:20:52.616
Bye! This was my plan.          
   That's my path.

472
00:20:52.651 --> 00:20:53.917
     [ Laughs ]

473
00:20:53.952 --> 00:21:04.728
                     ♪♪

474
